[
  {
    "startTime": 10.62,
    "endTime": 11.239999999999998,
    "text": "This war..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.18,
    "endTime": 12.82,
    "text": "We're not winning it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.16,
    "endTime": 17.54,
    "text": "If you speak a word of what I'm about to show you, you will be executed for high treason."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.42,
    "endTime": 18.92,
    "text": "It's beautiful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.78,
    "endTime": 24.240000000000002,
    "text": "It's the greatest encryption device in history and the Germans use it for all communications."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.5,
    "endTime": 26.46,
    "text": "Everyone thinks Enigma is unbreakable."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.92,
    "endTime": 28.700000000000003,
    "text": "Let me try and we'll know for sure."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.98,
    "endTime": 30.98,
    "text": "Mr. Turing, do you know how many died because of it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.24,
    "endTime": 33.78,
    "text": "I don't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.96,
    "endTime": 34.46,
    "text": "Three."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.22,
    "endTime": 36.66,
    "text": "While we've been having this conversation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.28,
    "endTime": 39.82,
    "text": "Gentlemen..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.96,
    "endTime": 40.54,
    "text": "Meet Mr. Turing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.76,
    "endTime": 41.879999999999995,
    "text": "We are to work together, then?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.02,
    "endTime": 43.580000000000005,
    "text": "I'm afraid these men would only slow me down."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.88,
    "endTime": 45.06,
    "text": "Popular at school, were you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.0,
    "endTime": 47.04,
    "text": "We're short on staff."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.24,
    "endTime": 48.480000000000004,
    "text": "We get more staff, then."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.18,
    "endTime": 52.28,
    "text": "You have six minutes to complete the task."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.54,
    "endTime": 53.42,
    "text": "Is that even possible?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.56,
    "endTime": 54.06,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.16,
    "endTime": 54.699999999999996,
    "text": "Takes me eight."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.44,
    "endTime": 57.919999999999995,
    "text": "Five minutes and thirty-four seconds."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.02,
    "endTime": 59.220000000000006,
    "text": "You said to do it in under six."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.54,
    "endTime": 61.8,
    "text": "What is it that we're really doing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.24,
    "endTime": 65.08,
    "text": "We're going to break an unbreakable Nazi code and win the war."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.5,
    "endTime": 66.0,
    "text": "Oh..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.14,
    "endTime": 72.4,
    "text": "You know, to pull off this irascible genius routine, one actually has to be a genius."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.9,
    "endTime": 77.68,
    "text": "I'm designing a machine that will allow us to break every message every day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.22,
    "endTime": 78.72,
    "text": "Instantly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.06,
    "endTime": 82.62,
    "text": "You're going to need all the help you can get."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.74,
    "endTime": 85.58,
    "text": "And they are not going to help you if they do not like you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.94,
    "endTime": 88.08,
    "text": "Have you decrypted a single German message?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.34,
    "endTime": 92.72,
    "text": "You will never understand the importance of what I am creating here!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.92,
    "endTime": 94.2,
    "text": "Our patience has expired."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.54,
    "endTime": 95.04,
    "text": "No!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.36,
    "endTime": 97.42,
    "text": "If you fire Alan..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.68,
    "endTime": 98.72000000000001,
    "text": "Well, then, you'll have to fire me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.2,
    "endTime": 99.86,
    "text": "Me, too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.0,
    "endTime": 100.58,
    "text": "And me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.18,
    "endTime": 102.42,
    "text": "It had better bloody work."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.02,
    "endTime": 106.83999999999999,
    "text": "Alan, you do not have to do this alone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.7,
    "endTime": 109.26,
    "text": "What are you doing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.44,
    "endTime": 109.94,
    "text": "What's going on?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.22,
    "endTime": 112.2,
    "text": "The Navy thinks that one of us is a Soviet spy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.74,
    "endTime": 114.44,
    "text": "You've got more secrets than the best of them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.18,
    "endTime": 117.16000000000001,
    "text": "What if I don't fancy her in that way?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.52,
    "endTime": 118.58,
    "text": "You can't tell anyone, Alan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.74,
    "endTime": 119.3,
    "text": "It's illegal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.54,
    "endTime": 125.64,
    "text": "I'm just a mathematician."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.1,
    "endTime": 129.06,
    "text": "Sometimes, it is the people who no one imagines anything of."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.96,
    "endTime": 132.42000000000002,
    "text": "Who do the things that no one..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.22,
    "endTime": 133.9,
    "text": "Can imagine."
  }
]